raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"photography_club_house\")
Naomi: img: mabel/112
Naomi: 👀
Player: Wow! 😳
Player: Is it going well?
Naomi: She claims she's never done anything like this before but I'm not buying it lol 😂
Player: Sounds like a yes 😄
Naomi: Your girl has a lot of hidden sex appeal 😏
Naomi: It's a super yes 😄
Naomi: And she's opening up about a few things to me 👀
Player: About??
Naomi: You can't just ask that, that's secret girl talk! 😉
Naomi: But I will say this, the way she talks about you seriously makes me a little jealous hehe 🥰
Player: 😳
Naomi: I think you'll find out soon 🤭
Naomi: Well we're about to have lunch now
Naomi: Ciao!
Player: Bye!
=> END"
